org.gephi.ranking.plugin
Class AbstractRanking<Element>

java.lang.Object
  org.gephi.ranking.plugin.AbstractRanking<Element>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Ranking<Element>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AttributeRankingBuilder.AttributeRanking, AttributeRankingBuilder.DynamicAttributeRanking
public abstract class AbstractRanking<Element>
extends Object
implements Ranking<Element>

Abstract ranking implementation, providing min/max storage.

It also has convenient static methods:

  • refreshMinMax: Refresh the minimum and maximum of the ranking for the given graph.
  • getMin: Returns the minimum of a Comparable array.
  • getMax: Returns the maximum of a Comparable array.

Author:
Mathieu Bastian
